data.description: Beautiful newly remodeled home. New exterior paint. New appliances (except the refrigerator). Beautiful tile flooring and kitchen backsplash. Space in basement could easily be a 4th bedroom or home office. Newer roof as well! Nice location with easy access to shopping, schools and highway access. Hardwood flooring under the carpet upstairs.
